{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_13_02",
  "title": "井川葵",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1755208749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します！　私、星見プロダクションの\n井川葵のマネージャーです",
      "startTime": 3.6662745722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.5666670482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ばぁば！　怪我したって聞いたけど\n大丈夫なの？",
      "startTime": 7.5333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.9333319346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba001.m4a",
      "text": "おや、葵ちゃん、そんなに慌ててどうしたんだい？\n敵情視察にでも来たのかい？",
      "startTime": 13.5488044938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　まさか葵の相手って……\nおばあちゃんアイドル『BEIJU』の……",
      "startTime": 19.4462561289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.0129234313
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、現役最高齢アイドル、DJばぁば\n僕のバトル相手だよ。言ってなかったっけ？",
      "startTime": 26.0333333969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.542174975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba002.m4a",
      "text": "あらあら葵ちゃん、マネージャーさんには\nちゃんと報告しなくちゃダメじゃない",
      "startTime": 33.2088410059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba003.m4a",
      "text": "報・連・相はアイドルの基本よ？　そういう日頃の\n地道な積み重ねが、あなたをもっと高みに押し上げるの",
      "startTime": 41.6088410059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.0421752293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん、そうだね。ばぁばの言う通りだ\nやっぱりばぁばはいいこと言うね。今後は気を付けるよ",
      "startTime": 51.6666667302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（俺が言っても全然響かないのに）\n（ばぁばさんの言うことは聞いてる……少しショックだ）",
      "startTime": 59.5000000636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.1180025737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、怪我したって聞いたから心配していたんだけど\n良かった。思ってたよりは元気そうだ",
      "startTime": 68.4846685013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.5839377721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba004.m4a",
      "text": "私が人生の荒波をいくつくぐり抜けてきたと\n思ってるの？　心配なんて無用だよ",
      "startTime": 76.583936882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そうはいかないよ。ベッドに横になって\n腰にはお灸までしてるんだから……本当に大丈夫？",
      "startTime": 84.6785927363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.0720826468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba005.m4a",
      "text": "今日のライブバトルが楽しみ過ぎて\n少しばかり、練習を張り切り過ぎちゃったかねぇ",
      "startTime": 93.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "残念ですけど……これじゃライブバトルは無理です\n葵、後日、ばぁばさんとは日を改めて再戦しよう",
      "startTime": 102.3638907448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.7054114025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba006.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの、マネージャーさん。このバトルを\n闘技場のみんなが楽しみに待ってるんだよ？",
      "startTime": 110.9387428284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.4054094951
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba007.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルがファンを失望させちゃダメよ\n葵ちゃんだって、私と同じ気持ちなんじゃない？",
      "startTime": 119.4054094951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、僕だってアイドルだからね\nばぁばの気持ちは痛いくらいに分かるよ",
      "startTime": 127.4666591008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.0746301652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "応援してくれるファンに応えたい……\nその想いは、野良アイドルもプロも関係ないから",
      "startTime": 134.0666692734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、その体でライブバトルをするのは難しい\n今のばぁばは、支えがないと立つことさえ出来ないんだ",
      "startTime": 143.5666814805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.8078759513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ。僕がばぁばをステージで支える\nっていうのはどうかな？",
      "startTime": 152.300003624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.060302067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba008.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、アイドルっていうより\n孫に介護されるおばあちゃんだよ",
      "startTime": 157.6936309499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "でも他にいい方法は思いつかないよ\n体を壊したら元も子もないし、やっぱり今日は……",
      "startTime": 165.4269627334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.462472884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba009.m4a",
      "text": "葵ちゃん、私はアイドルだよ\nアイドルがステージで死ねるなら、本望なんだ",
      "startTime": 176.5291412038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.6957990965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "その言葉、ばぁばさんが言うと重みが違うので\n止めて下さい……",
      "startTime": 183.5624745371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba010.m4a",
      "text": "私はね、八十年以上生きてきて大事な日に休んだことは\n一度もないの。今の夢は生涯現役アイドルでいることよ",
      "startTime": 191.1624745371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.1333485921
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "生涯現役……か。ばぁばは、その命が尽きるまで\nずっとステージに立ち続けるつもりなんだね……凄いな",
      "startTime": 204.6666865667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 210.2468661946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……仕方ない。葵、一つだけ方法がある\n葵には無茶なお願いをすることになるが……",
      "startTime": 214.9135568939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 218.1801995279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}君。僕、どんな無茶でもやる\nだから、どうすればいいか教えて",
      "startTime": 222.5000199001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4124.262142300012,
          "startTime": 226.6242820424
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 226.3742820424
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 226.3742820424
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 226.6242820424
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 232.3666865667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
