      "text": "みんな、この間ぶりだね。僕のこと覚えてる？\n僕の名前は井が……じゃない、アオアオ……だっけ？",
      "startTime": 232.3666865667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（……本名を言いかけてるし、芸名は忘れかけてるし）\n（……不安だ……）",
      "startTime": 244.7727185889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 246.1060400965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba011.m4a",
      "text": "元気かい、みんな。今日の私は『BEIJU』じゃない\nただのDJばぁばとして、みんなに会いに来たよ",
      "startTime": 251.0393974625,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 246.1060400965
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、僕達のライブバトルの予定だったんだけど\n急遽、二人でユニットを組んで歌うことにしたんだ",
      "startTime": 259.8333532334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 263.7998577438
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "僕はバトルも好きだけど、歌うのも大好きでね\nばぁばと僕のデュエット、聴いてもらえるかな",
      "startTime": 268.0666865667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
