      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（客席からの見え方まで計算しないと、出来ない芸当だ）\n（葵には無茶を頼んだけど、良くやってくれた）",
      "startTime": 283.5809042617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
