      "bgName": "prowrestlingring-00-noon",
      "startTime": 286.9475448611
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、歌うよ。振り付けも僕が考えたんだ\n簡単だから、良かったら一緒に踊ってほしい",
      "startTime": 291.5000199001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、ばぁば、もっと僕に体重かけて\n……そうそう、それなら腰を痛めずに踊れるでしょ？",
      "startTime": 301.3011595405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "うん、カッコいいね。さすがは最高齢アイドルだ\n僕らとは年季が違うね",
      "startTime": 310.9773765766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（そして、葵に即興で作ってもらったこの振り付け）\n（ばぁばさんに負担をかけないように考えられている）",
      "startTime": 318.0883579259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（多くの縛りがある中、これほどの振り付けを）\n（用意出来るとは……やっぱり、葵のダンスは超一流だ）",
      "startTime": 324.7216892247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "djba",
      "speakerName": "DJばぁば",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-djba012.m4a",
      "text": "葵ちゃん、即興でこんな振り付けが出来るなんて\nやっぱり凄い子だねぇ……私には絶対に出来やしないよ",
      "startTime": 335.2883314773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの。ばぁばがいたから、このダンスが\n生まれたんだ。僕一人の力じゃない",
      "startTime": 345.8015051856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "ファンを笑顔にしたい。生涯アイドルでいたい\nそんなばぁばの強い想いが、この振り付けを生んだんだ",
      "startTime": 353.6982173807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_13_02-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "僕、ばぁばみたいに、ファンを強く思いやれる\nアイドルに、大人に……なるよ",
      "startTime": 362.2999771754,
      "sfxList": []
    }
